Sentencas: The high performance and robust durability of electrode materials are crucial requirements for intermediatetemperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Nd3+-deficiency double perovskite Nd1-xBaCo2O5+s and performance optimization as cathode materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This study prepared a new type of Nd1-xBaCo2O5+s+x/2Bi2O3 (x = 0.05, 0.1; NBC95+B, NBC90+B) composite cathode materials by introducing an Nd defect with bismuth oxide.
Titulo: Nd3+-deficiency double perovskite Nd1-xBaCo2O5+s and performance optimization as cathode materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The introduction of a bismuth oxide trace effectively increased conductivity and reduced the thermal expansion coefficient.
Titulo: Nd3+-deficiency double perovskite Nd1-xBaCo2O5+s and performance optimization as cathode materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The polarization impedance and maximum power density of the NBC95+B cathode were 0.026 omega cm-2 and 720 mW cm-2 at 800 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Nd3+-deficiency double perovskite Nd1-xBaCo2O5+s and performance optimization as cathode materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The good electrochemical performance of the NBC95+B composite cathode is attributed to the introduction of Nd cation defects and the sub-oxidation state of Bi cations.
Titulo: Nd3+-deficiency double perovskite Nd1-xBaCo2O5+s and performance optimization as cathode materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Furthermore, the NBC95+B cathode exhibited good resistance to carbon dioxide poisoning.
Titulo: Nd3+-deficiency double perovskite Nd1-xBaCo2O5+s and performance optimization as cathode materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
